<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 18:09:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>佛蒙特州伯灵顿男子因涉嫌仇恨犯罪枪杀三名巴勒斯坦学生而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/man-arrested-for-shooting-three-palestinian-students-in-u-s-in-suspected-hate-crime/0000018c-117f-dd03-a7ff-bf7fd9da0000</link><description>枪击事件发生之际，穆斯林和阿拉伯裔美国人的权利和倡导团体报告称，针对阿拉伯人和穆斯林美国人的仇恨犯罪史无前例地激增</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 16:29:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/man-arrested-for-shooting-three-palestinian-students-in-u-s-in-suspected-hate-crime/0000018c-117f-dd03-a7ff-bf7fd9da0000</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯裔以色列人质逃离哈马斯囚禁，在当地人抓住他之前躲在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/russian-israeli-hostage-escaped-hamas-captivity-hid-in-gaza-before-locals-caught-him/0000018c-1121-dd2e-a5ae-d36bfcc40000</link><description>俄罗斯裔以色列人罗尼·克里沃伊 (Roni Krivoi) 是迄今为止唯一获释的成年男性人质，他成功逃离哈马斯几天，但最终在周日被抓获并释放回以色列</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 16:21:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/russian-israeli-hostage-escaped-hamas-captivity-hid-in-gaza-before-locals-caught-him/0000018c-1121-dd2e-a5ae-d36bfcc40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列著名人​​权组织敦促国际刑事法院对哈马斯的强奸和其他性犯罪行为进行调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/prominent-israeli-rights-group-urges-icc-probe-of-hamas-for-rape-and-other-sex-crimes/0000018c-1168-dd03-a7ff-bf78860e0000</link><description>这份由以色列人权医生组织发表的论文提供了哈马斯 10 月 7 日涉嫌性犯罪和基于性别的犯罪的详细清单，这些犯罪已被记录并公开分享。根据已知的情况，该文件得出的结论是，此类暴行“普遍存在”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 16:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/prominent-israeli-rights-group-urges-icc-probe-of-hamas-for-rape-and-other-sex-crimes/0000018c-1168-dd03-a7ff-bf78860e0000</guid></item><item><title>获释的以色列人质让我们得以一睹加沙哈马斯俘虏的生活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/freed-israeli-hostages-offer-glimpse-of-life-in-gaza-as-hamas-captives/0000018c-10fc-d679-abdc-96fcf16d0000</link><description>与 40 名获释人质的家人的对话提供了他们在加沙经历的第一批细节。大多数人被关在隧道里，而其他人则被关在房屋和建筑物中，并担心遭到炮击。有人听到了一项特别的公告来纪念他的九岁生日</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 15:46:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/freed-israeli-hostages-offer-glimpse-of-life-in-gaza-as-hamas-captives/0000018c-10fc-d679-abdc-96fcf16d0000</guid></item><item><title>被哈马斯扣为人质的以色列儿童从加沙获释后开始分享他们的经历</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/freed-from-gaza-israeli-children-held-hostage-by-hamas-begin-to-share-their-experiences/0000018c-10e1-d679-abdc-96f9d9590000</link><description>一些人质返回失去亲人的家庭、无家可归的家庭和支离破碎的社区，同时继续为仍被哈马斯扣押的亲人的安全感到焦虑</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 15:05:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/freed-from-gaza-israeli-children-held-hostage-by-hamas-begin-to-share-their-experiences/0000018c-10e1-d679-abdc-96f9d9590000</guid></item><item><title>“战争永远是地狱”：道德哲学家谈以色列在加沙行动的伦理</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/war-is-always-hell-moral-philosophers-on-the-ethics-of-israels-battle-with-hamas/0000018c-10b8-d2ae-afcf-35fabe230000</link><description>上个月，牛津大学的40多名学者谴责了以色列国防军在加沙的行动，引发了六位以色列道德哲学家的反驳。在那次交流之后，专家们讨论了战争中什么是“相称的”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 14:06:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/war-is-always-hell-moral-philosophers-on-the-ethics-of-israels-battle-with-hamas/0000018c-10b8-d2ae-afcf-35fabe230000</guid></item><item><title>德国媒体强调柏林“积极”参与释放哈马斯人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/german-media-emphasizes-berlins-intensive-involvement-in-the-release-of-hamas-hostages/0000018c-107c-d65f-a7dd-f0ffa5370000</link><description>据《南德意志报》报道，德国向以色列派遣了“军事和情报部门”，帮助寻找具有德国公民身份的人质，德国外交官“与卡塔尔保持着持续联系”。前总理亚伊尔·拉皮德告诉《犹太汇报》：“这也是你们的战争”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 12:46:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/german-media-emphasizes-berlins-intensive-involvement-in-the-release-of-hamas-hostages/0000018c-107c-d65f-a7dd-f0ffa5370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯的人质交易帮助卡塔尔在10月7日之后改善其形象</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/the-hostage-deal-is-helping-qatar-rehabilitate-its-image-after-the-blow-of-october-7/0000018c-1043-d679-abdc-967bffa90000</link><description>10 月 7 日大屠杀之后，由于该国与哈马斯的关系，卡塔尔的形象受到打击。现在，它在导致以色列人质获释的协议中所发挥的作用正在赢得美国和以色列的赞扬</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 12:42:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/the-hostage-deal-is-helping-qatar-rehabilitate-its-image-after-the-blow-of-october-7/0000018c-1043-d679-abdc-967bffa90000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡关于哈马斯的错误前提在开罗找到了合作伙伴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-false-premise-about-hamas-had-a-partner-in-cairo/0000018c-101c-dd2e-a5ae-d35f0b4b0000</link><description>塞西将自己定位为以色列和哈马斯之间的唯一调解人，并与内塔尼亚胡一起宣扬“金钱会带来和平”的虚假前提。现在，他们必须为后哈马斯加沙的“后天”制定计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 11:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-false-premise-about-hamas-had-a-partner-in-cairo/0000018c-101c-dd2e-a5ae-d35f0b4b0000</guid></item><item><title>操纵大师班：揭露马克斯·布卢门撒尔关于以色列和 10 月 7 日的谎言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article-opinion/exposing-max-blumenthals-deceptive-claim-israel-is-responsible-for-most-october-7-victims/0000018c-102f-d65f-a7dd-f0ff7b550000</link><description>灰色地带的编辑有否认战争罪的历史，所以毫不奇怪他提供了一篇非常有选择性地使用事实的文章，包括故意编辑的引文以改变其含义，并严重淡化针对以色列人的暴行</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 10:43:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article-opinion/exposing-max-blumenthals-deceptive-claim-israel-is-responsible-for-most-october-7-victims/0000018c-102f-d65f-a7dd-f0ff7b550000</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克在加沙停火期间访问以色列并会见内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/elon-musk-visits-israel-amid-gaza-cease-fire-will-meet-with-netanyahu/0000018c-0fec-d65f-a7dd-ffffd6fe0000</link><description>X 所有者可能会讨论在以色列和加沙运营星链卫星。以色列通讯部长 X 表示，“它只能在以色列通讯部批准的情况下在以色列运营”</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 09:35:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/elon-musk-visits-israel-amid-gaza-cease-fire-will-meet-with-netanyahu/0000018c-0fec-d65f-a7dd-ffffd6fe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部考虑如何起诉哈马斯恐怖分子以及可能使用死刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-ministry-mulls-how-to-prosecute-hamas-terrorists-in-court/0000018c-0c00-d679-abdc-9e387c500000</link><description>由于哈马斯 10 月 7 日大屠杀的性质和规模，以色列司法部面临重大挑战。选择包括集体起诉、军事法庭审判和种族灭绝起诉</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 09:34:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-ministry-mulls-how-to-prosecute-hamas-terrorists-in-court/0000018c-0c00-d679-abdc-9e387c500000</guid></item><item><title>停战期间，加沙人收集尸体、揭露破坏、寻找亲人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/during-truce-gazans-gather-bodies-reveal-destruction-seek-relatives/0000018c-0fe5-d65f-a7dd-fff742d10000</link><description>经过七周的轰炸后，停火使加沙人民能够近距离检查他们家园的废墟，或者至少尝试接近他们</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 09:14:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/during-truce-gazans-gather-bodies-reveal-destruction-seek-relatives/0000018c-0fe5-d65f-a7dd-fff742d10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总理办公室更新了预计将于周一获释的人质家属的最新情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article-live/hamas-seeks-longer-cease-fire-as-sides-enter-final-day-of-swap-39-israelis-freed-so-far/0000018c-0ef1-d679-abdc-9ef9589f0000</link><description>卡塔尔宣布停火期限延长两天，以色列总理办公室表示，预计将于周一晚间获释的人质家属已获得最新消息 ■ 84 岁以色列人质获释后入院治疗，生命垂危 ■ 哈马斯寻求延长停火期限停火 ■ 拜登表示，美国计划将战斗暂停时间延长至周一之后 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵丧生；加沙仍有 200 多名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：加沙有 14,854 人死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 04:46:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article-live/hamas-seeks-longer-cease-fire-as-sides-enter-final-day-of-swap-39-israelis-freed-so-far/0000018c-0ef1-d679-abdc-9ef9589f0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯停火结束后，以色列军队计划扩大加沙攻势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-army-plans-to-resume-offense-on-hamas-in-gaza-once-cease-fire-ends/0000018c-0d1b-d65f-a7dd-fddfd93a0000</link><description>以色列军队决定将行动范围扩大到加沙南部，那里的哈马斯状况要好得多。以色列希望停火让哈马斯有机会看到北部地带的破坏，这可能会削弱继续战斗的动力</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 04:27:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-army-plans-to-resume-offense-on-hamas-in-gaza-once-cease-fire-ends/0000018c-0d1b-d65f-a7dd-fddfd93a0000</guid></item><item><title>在相互压力下，以色列向哈马斯发出信号，如果更多人质获释，则不急于恢复加沙战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-signals-to-hamas-no-rush-to-resume-gaza-fighting-if-more-hostages-freed/0000018c-0d75-ddff-a3bc-bdf5e82f0000</link><description>哈马斯对延长停火协议非常感兴趣，该组织告诉卡塔尔人，它将尝试寻找更多符合协议首要标准的以色列人，其中包括约 90 人。以色列国防军也需要时间来更新其部队并为下一阶段做好准备</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 04:27:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-signals-to-hamas-no-rush-to-resume-gaza-fighting-if-more-hostages-freed/0000018c-0d75-ddff-a3bc-bdf5e82f0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-27/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-0eaa-d2ae-afcf-3ffacb480000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 02:49:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-27/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-0eaa-d2ae-afcf-3ffacb480000</guid></item><item><title>是时候废除以色列政府多余且成本高昂的部门了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-27/ty-article/time-to-scrap-the-israeli-governments-countless-redundant-ministries/0000018c-0d5a-ddff-a3bc-bdfebaae0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 00:07:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-27/ty-article/time-to-scrap-the-israeli-governments-countless-redundant-ministries/0000018c-0d5a-ddff-a3bc-bdfebaae0000</guid></item><item><title>针对以色列德鲁兹公民的特别法律？不，谢谢</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/a-special-law-for-israels-druze-citizens-no-thanks/0000018c-0cfb-d65f-a7dd-fcff89a40000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 23:08:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/a-special-law-for-israels-druze-citizens-no-thanks/0000018c-0cfb-d65f-a7dd-fcff89a40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列试图阻止巴勒斯坦囚犯获释的庆祝活动揭示了战争的真正目的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-bid-to-stop-celebration-of-prisoners-release-reveals-real-aim-of-war/0000018c-0cfb-d2ae-afcf-3dfb8abb0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 22:02:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-bid-to-stop-celebration-of-prisoners-release-reveals-real-aim-of-war/0000018c-0cfb-d2ae-afcf-3dfb8abb0000</guid></item></channel></rss>